{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC15_TAN_510.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x25,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, do you think you can tell me about the city again?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yup, sure. Tanya, you really are curious about the city, huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I've been getting even more curious since I started listening to your stories."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Tanya, have you ever been to Hornheim...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Nooope, I haven't. I've heard it's a city by the shore..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then I'll tell you about Hornheim. Let's see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hornheim is a port town that prospers through trade. Various items and people from all over the world..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Travel there by hot air balloon or carriage. Your salt gets delivered there, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "The items that flow into Hornheim are bought by merchants, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "From there, they're delivered to different towns."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I see...so there are a lot of other cities... Umm, are there like five?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I'm not too sure, but I think there are more."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "But from the ones I've seen, Vierzeberg is the biggest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "A lot of my friends live there,<CR>and there are just so many people."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh, you told me about Vierzeberg last time, and that it's a big city."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Yup. I used to live all alone to the east of Vierzeberg..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "So when I first got there, I was so surprised. There are big bridges and it's surrounded by high walls."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "There are lots of buildings, too. There are a bunch of shops along the streets that sell a lot of different things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "But even with all that, the most amazing thing about it is the bazaar."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "What's a bazaar...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "It's held once a month, and people who don't usually have a store can open up a shop."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "And people come from all across the land to look for lucky finds."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I guess you could find some very rare items there."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "People say that there's nothing that you can't find at the bazaar."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Wow, that sounds amazing...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'm glad I got to listen to another one of your stories. Thank you so much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "All of your stories have sounded amazing, but this bazaar is the best one so far!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I know it's a little far, but you should go see it someday."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x185,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I wonder...<CR>I wonder if I could really go there..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x187,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Oh, and I...have one more favor to ask you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Huh? What is it? Don't be shy, you can ask me anything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Well, I don't care what it is, but I really want something from the city."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "But since I can't go to the city<CR>myself, I was hoping you could buy<CR>me something..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Uh, you can do it whenever you have the time. I can't buy anything expensive..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Sure. I'll look for something that you might like."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Wow! Thank you so much!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "(Okay, I should look for something the next time I go to Vierzeberg.)"
        }
    ]
}